channel.description: hello guys im here to give some help to newbies that are just starting servers, or need help with stuff. Im not the best coder but i know a lot. I can help people other then newbies but may not be able to do stuff you need. Ill try my best to help. If you need help just pm me or post back. i only do server sided stuff. Ps: i can also set you up some basic free forums!
